org.apache.river.test.impl.outrigger.matching

Class FieldMatchTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.river.qa.harness.QATestEnvironment

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Test, TestEnvironment
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FieldMatchTestNBE, FieldMatchTestUniqueEntry, FieldMatchTestUseIfExists, FieldMatchTestUseIfExistsShutdown

    public class FieldMatchTest
extends MatchTestBase
    JavaSpace matching test that writes a number of entries and then takes them all using a template that will match all of the written entries. Test is only passed if the space is empty after all the takes and there are only as many successful takes as writes.
